      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "What about (same logic, reduces the number of GetBoolArg calls to one for each option):\n\n``` c++\n    if (GetBoolArg(\"-sysperms\", false)) {\n#ifdef ENABLE_WALLET\n        if (!GetBoolArg(\"-disablewallet\", false))\n            return InitError(\"E....\")\n#endif\n    } else {\n        umask(077);\n    }\n```\n",
      "commit_id" : "7e09b36ea5316671dfc86df62d90f78597b22fe9",
      "created_at" : "2014-06-08T16:12:51Z",
      "diff_hunk" : "@@ -422,7 +425,17 @@ bool AppInit2(boost::thread_group& threadGroup)\n     }\n #endif\n #ifndef WIN32\n-    umask(077);\n+\n+#ifdef ENABLE_WALLET\n+    if (!GetBoolArg(\"-sysperms\", false) || !GetBoolArg(\"-disablewallet\", false)) {\n+        umask(077);\n+        if (GetBoolArg(\"-sysperms\", false))\n+            return InitError(\"Error: -sysperms is not allowed in combination with enabled wallet functionality\");\n+    }\n+#else\n+    if (!GetBoolArg(\"-sysperms\", false))\n+        umask(077);\n+#endif",
      "html_url" : "https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/4286#discussion_r13524881",
